version_description: From Live at "Music Planet 2nite" .Acoustic, from my guitar pro tab. Live version, more complete than the other album version.
You'll need to use your thumb on the low E string for the Dm/F and D7/F# chords.
I decided to completely chord this with my own selection from what I heard. I play it arpeggiated.

version_description: Thumb on the low E string creates a nice bass progression for Adim/F# Asus4/F and D/F#.
This version attempts to account for all the little variations Thom does when playing this, and add accuracy. Shoutout to versions one and three which I used as a guide.
